&lt;h2>🚀 Level 1: Python Fundamentals&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="-level-1-python-fundamentals">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#-level-1-python-fundamentals" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;h3>✅ Basic Syntax &amp;amp; Data Types&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="-basic-syntax--data-types">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#-basic-syntax--data-types" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Variables and data types (&lt;code>int&lt;/code>, &lt;code>float&lt;/code>, &lt;code>str&lt;/code>, &lt;code>bool&lt;/code>, &lt;code>list&lt;/code>, &lt;code>tuple&lt;/code>, &lt;code>set&lt;/code>, &lt;code>dict&lt;/code>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Arithmetic operations (&lt;code>+&lt;/code>, &lt;code>-&lt;/code>, &lt;code>*&lt;/code>, &lt;code>/&lt;/code>, &lt;code>//&lt;/code>, &lt;code>%&lt;/code>, &lt;code>**&lt;/code>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Input and Output (&lt;code>input()&lt;/code>, &lt;code>print()&lt;/code>)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
